## Test Scenario 8 — Edge Cases & Error Handling

| # | Test | Steps | Expected Result |
|---|------|-------|-----------------|
| 1 | **Empty JD** | Open modal → leave JD blank → try to upload | "Create & Upload" button stays disabled |
| 2 | **JD too short** | Type < 50 characters | Shows character counter, button disabled |
| 3 | **No files** | Fill JD but don't upload files | Button disabled (needs both JD + files) |
| 4 | **Wrong file type** | Try dragging a `.txt` or `.jpg` file | File rejected — not added to list |
| 5 | **Modal escape** | Press `Escape` while modal is open | Modal closes cleanly |
| 6 | **Modal backdrop click** | Click outside the modal | Modal closes cleanly |
| 7 | **Sign out** | Click **"Sign out"** in the header | User logged out → redirected to `/` |
| 8 | **Error dismissal** | If an error appears, click the ✕ button | Error banner dismissed |
| 9 | **Mobile nav** | On mobile viewport, test hamburger menu | Nav items + sign out appear in dropdown |

